analysis.description:
Sale.Sale (/unique_chucks/5/0x94dc1cf66c8fd62ef3bd7da53f47423862839823.sol#322-345) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- assert(bool)(token.balanceOf(this) == token.totalSupply())
	- assert(bool)(token.balanceOf(this) == _tokenSupply)
